Manual Test Scenarios:
----------------------

1. Validate input range for w,x,y,z variables as per defined ranges.
    i.   0<w<=20
    ii.  x<=0 || x>w
    iii. y<=0 || y>w
    iv.  z<=0 || z>w
    v.   (x+y+z)>w
    
2. Validate letters used for creating word meets criteria of defined ranges.
3. Validate if the words created using parameters x,y,z,w is a palindrome or not.